verbose_text: Ammonium acetate enhanced the hyperammonaemic action of cyclophosphamide while promoting its lethal action : the mean survival time decreased 1.5, 2.1, 2.8, or 6.1 times at the background of cyclophosphamide i/p doses 200, 600, 1000, or 1400 mg/kg, respectively.
evidence: Ammonium acetate enhanced the hyperammonaemic action of cyclophosphamide
